ED_Title: Programme planning (Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee))
ED_DecisionText:
At its 53rd plenary meeting, on 6 December 2016, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee. 

(See A/71/504, A/71/PV.53)
